The NeuroSky MindWave device did not come with a Java implementation.

I created this library to make it easy to communicate with the ThinkGear connector over Java sockets, both in Processing and in Eclipse.

A processing example is provided.

Make sure the thinkgear connector is running. 

/Andreas Borg

Read more
https://crea.tion.to/thinkgear-java-socket/


Added a zipped Eclipse project version tested with Processing 2.0b9 in examples folder

